        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Used Car Safety Recall Repair Act</b></p> <p>Prohibits a dealer from selling or leasing a used passenger motor vehicle until a defect of the motor vehicle or motor vehicle equipment or noncompliance with a federal motor vehicle safety standard has been remedied.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
